==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Simplesse
<hw>Sim"plesse</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a trade name for a
fat substitute prepared as microparticles of protein from whey. It has
little fat, but has a consistency and taste resembling fat, and is thus
used to prepare foods low in fat for dietetic purposes.</def>
<mark>[Trade name]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Simpleton</ent>⟦br⟧
